X_t
\int_0^t \exp(\alpha X_{s^-})dX_s.
\int_0^t \exp(\alpha X_{s^-})dX_s=\frac1{e^{\alpha}-1}[\exp(\alpha X_t)-1],
\mathbb{E} \exp(\alpha X_t)=\exp\{\lambda t (e^{\alpha}-1)\}
